# 📚 Vault Structure



```

{{PRIMARY_VAULT_PATH}}

├── sessions/

│   └── YYYY-MM/              # Monthly directories

│       └── session-slug.md   # Conversation summaries

├── topics/

│   └── topic-name.md         # Technical documentation

├── decisions/

│   └── NNNN-decision-title.md # ADRs (numbered)

├── projects/

│   └── [project-slug]/

│       ├── project.md        # Project overview

│       └── commits/

│           └── [hash].md     # Individual commits

└── archive/                  # Archived/stale content

```



**File organization:**

- Sessions: Organized by year-month (`2025-01/`, `2025-02/`)

- Topics: Flat structure with descriptive slugs

- Decisions: **Hierarchical by scope** (vault-level or project-specific)
  - `decisions/vault/` - MCP system decisions
  - `decisions/{project-slug}/` - Project-specific decisions
  - Each scope has independent numbering (001, 002, ...)

- Projects: One directory per Git repository

- Commits: Nested under their project



